{"tid":289152,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[龍貓奴] 屋企隻龍貓唔肯食草食乾糧","createTime":"2017-06-18T17:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T22:38:29.000Z","uid":5788,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cbc4d82cb6c81b35597b9fbca4e06918d94ea8","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:47:04.000Z","msg":"我隻龍貓因爲門牙同入面啲牙過長 長到會整到隻眼所以會定期帶佢去剪牙<br />\n問題係佢剪完牙一排都係唔肯點食乾糧同草 咬兩咬就唔食 咁我唯有餵佢食草粉<br />\n但係我上網睇話草粉太多營養啲牙會生得快啲<br />\n有咩方法可以迫到佢食草等佢可以磨到內牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06a9ba9818c47529884a086415d594338408149","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c89944ade662f12ca00f026896f35c8ec0d1be6a","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"e360ee3751975b3d59fe3489d5bc6cc443ec2fc4","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d7e5c3274c58cdf8353f0da4519420be49ec21d","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42626ca10f49fcff52b1f1cc433c38556b519cae","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal