nail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F020030_e640470c832fadae9efbe691e26aa044.jpg&h=bca2b510&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/020031_3f2d5db5fb9b5699b46bf0db2b52fb4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F020031_3f2d5db5fb9b5699b46bf0db2b52fb4b.jpg&h=9c76b06a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c895ed2853bfcf7c0242e983dacb2150771352c","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"好想佢可以好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbb5a6685cd06c4605c865e4bc5f5b302f81df0","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c10c2bb7f24ba864a6eda949240a461de716be8","tid":289152,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72649cb6244003e6ee044a48fd0f489dc8a53069","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家LIHKG自推唔會上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8a06ba007628c946a468ffd483984cb83bf724","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b39a3b1eeb8162bea736c8db0fa07b206f4eea","tid":289152,"uid":66340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T18:07:32.000Z","msg":"無人識龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e48aa3dca0c7ba9a40d8f5a51a2fb6440cfef81","tid":289152,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:08:36.000Z","msg":"問醫生啦<br />\n但佢唔食野都係要喂草粉比佢<br />\n會唔會嫌草過硬個d 之前個d黃d都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯食野亦都可能係身體有其他問題<br />\n唔係專業好難答你<br />\n利申 冇養過龍貓 淨係養過天竺鼠<br />\n<br />\n小動物唔食野好快會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  快d睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"3c1404a72ec8df2f6890f6deed7dc41c78b351e2","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T21:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻龍貓因爲門牙同入面啲牙過長 長到會整到隻眼所以會定期帶佢去剪牙<br />\n問題係佢剪完牙一排都係唔肯點食乾糧同草 咬兩咬就唔食 咁我唯有餵佢食草粉<br />\n但係我上網睇話草粉太多營養啲牙會生得快啲<br />\n有咩方法可以迫到佢食草等佢可以磨到內牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾耐之前剪牙？<br />\n食草粉係為左維持住個基本重量同埋補充能量姐。<br />\n至於迫佢食草既話就要減零食同減糧，逐步減，同埋可以試下轉草既牌子同轉食2nd cut"},{"pid":"66c23ce15d3f45ec06fa4476dd3b6b1762bf6c20","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我隻龍貓因爲門牙同入面啲牙過長 長到會整到隻眼所以會定期帶佢去剪牙<br />\n問題係佢剪完牙一排都係唔肯點食乾糧同草 咬兩咬就唔食 咁我唯有餵佢食草粉<br />\n但係我上網睇話草粉太多營養啲牙會生得快啲<br />\n有咩方法可以迫到佢食草等佢可以磨到內牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾耐之前剪牙？<br />\n食草粉係為左維持住個基本重量同埋補充能量姐。<br />\n至於迫佢食草既話就要減零食同減糧，逐步減，同埋可以試下轉草既牌子同轉食2nd cut</blockquote><br />\n啱啱個星期日剪完<br />\n我有餵草粉不過唔多 個籠都有擺乾糧同草不過佢冇乜意欲食<br />\n佢以前一直食開timothy hay<br />\n巴打有冇咩牌子介紹"},{"pid":"5739d2989825c1b5b46cda82d7740957c5db3d81","tid":289152,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"oxford嘅Timothy hay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbbe13a891db70e0353b35d7d8bdc18c892476a","tid":289152,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"你只可以餓治 唔可以唔忍心畀其他野佢食"},{"pid":"3c1d17594c5ffcf0485c8691553a9f233f9edbdf","tid":289152,"uid":100817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:31:24.000Z","msg":"係咪D牙唔舒服呀？唔係點會無啦啦唔食野<br />\n<br />\n我記得細個養龍貓個時要買埋舊磨牙石比佢咬<br />\n一直都唔知有剪牙呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫推，希望有人解答到樓主"},{"pid":"613766e76a1d26d370db89cffef7c3011d4abd45","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我隻龍貓因爲門牙同入面啲牙過長 長到會整到隻眼所以會定期帶佢去剪牙<br />\n問題係佢剪完牙一排都係唔肯點食乾糧同草 咬兩咬就唔食 咁我唯有餵佢食草粉<br />\n但係我上網睇話草粉太多營養啲牙會生得快啲<br />\n有咩方法可以迫到佢食草等佢可以磨到內牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾耐之前剪牙？<br />\n食草粉係為左維持住個基本重量同埋補充能量姐。<br />\n至於迫佢食草既話就要減零食同減糧，逐步減，同埋可以試下轉草既牌子同轉食2nd cut</blockquote><br />\n啱啱個星期日剪完<br />\n我有餵草粉不過唔多 個籠都有擺乾糧同草不過佢冇乜意欲食<br />\n佢以前一直食開timothy hay<br />\n巴打有冇咩牌子介紹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩星期日姐係琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTimothy hay係草名黎，定係你買個牌子真係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw糧唔需要長期24小時都有供應，如果食草量足夠，其實糧比唔比都得"},{"pid":"48f994de2653cbc1fc061fdba51c1955cfaab39a","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"絲打我依家就比開momi 1st佢食，貪呢個牌子長期有貨，不過質素唔算十分穩定<br />\n以前磅數唔夠果陣就買wooly 一番割，不過好L貴同埋成日無貨，但係食左1年之後胃口好似真係好左同大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係轉草既話記得慢慢轉唔好一下轉哂，可以逐啲溝等佢適應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來連登真係無人養龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd00655021bf20430ed2015599f9559ca2a4b41e","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>oxford嘅Timothy hay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇外國網話近期oxford既Timothy hay好似出左問題，巴打小心啲"},{"pid":"591bfaecd88dfd10eb78160c471e6c86a1e59b0f","tid":289152,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7b085fb42c273a25ff4daa996374dc913c1c86c","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會試下轉下草同狠心啲餓下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf3e837965a04272fb1a14a735846d848b6ab67","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能剪完牙 牙痛無胃口食草<br />\n有錢就再帶佢去檢查下  問下醫生意見<br />\n<br />\n或者你自己剪短啲啲草/揀多啲葉出黎比龍貓食<br />\n等佢有返胃口之後買仙人掌木/蘋果木/硬草餅比佢keep住磨牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋間草莓屋小心龍貓𠝹到，祝吉貓天相 平平安安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張相入面間屋係以前架啦個陣佢乜事都未有<br />\n而家轉左新屋唔會𠝹到佢放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThx:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f094c2f4642a0d862992a1bf382a66a084a393ff","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會試下轉下草同狠心啲餓下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你隻龍貓幾重啊？<br />\n同埋糧一日最多比一隻外賣匙既份量就夠了，希望你隻龍貓快啲好番啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4340bda6c2d175db91b7e2227098f8ce423892e","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我隻龍貓因爲門牙同入面啲牙過長 長到會整到隻眼所以會定期帶佢去剪牙<br />\n問題係佢剪完牙一排都係唔肯點食乾糧同草 咬兩咬就唔食 咁我唯有餵佢食草粉<br />\n但係我上網睇話草粉太多營養啲牙會生得快啲<br />\n有咩方法可以迫到佢食草等佢可以磨到內牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾耐之前剪牙？<br />\n食草粉係為左維持住個基本重量同埋補充能量姐。<br />\n至於迫佢食草既話就要減零食同減糧，逐步減，同埋可以試下轉草既牌子同轉食2nd cut</blockquote><br />\n啱啱個星期日剪完<br />\n我有餵草粉不過唔多 個籠都有擺乾糧同草不過佢冇乜意欲食<br />\n佢以前一直食開timothy hay<br />\n巴打有冇咩牌子介紹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩星期日姐係琴日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTimothy hay係草名黎，定係你買個牌子真係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw糧唔需要長期24小時都有供應，如果食草量足夠，其實糧比唔比都得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢其實之前已經剪過幾次牙 每次剪完牙我都係餵草粉 唔知係咪因爲咁佢習慣左食草粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今日開始冇再俾草粉佢 俾左糧同草 <br />\n陣間番屋企睇下佢有冇食到"},{"pid":"3bf8e1a5e18af21898ddc9398087b171a247b80b","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"話說我琴晚擺低左堆草俾佢<br />\n第二朝我發覺佢喺上面屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪代表呢款佢唔鍾意要買過新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be0d4474d17e25706b37dc23a38064cffa29719","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會試下轉下草同狠心啲餓下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打你隻龍貓幾重啊？<br />\n同埋糧一日最多比一隻外賣匙既份量就夠了，希望你隻龍貓快啲好番啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上星期日睇醫生磅左係512g<br />\n我見佢咬兩咬就丟低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574de5f1afc91bc6743e334127826562ba5fb59f","tid":289152,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話說我琴晚擺低左堆草俾佢<br />\n第二朝我發覺佢喺上面屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪代表呢款佢唔鍾意要買過新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剪完牙頭幾日要食草粉係正常架<br />\n疴尿係草上面我果隻閒唔時都會，不過我無理佢，還掂都要每日換草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3750809fa6a046c80881652f7a860beeb4adb1a4","tid":289152,"uid":5788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話說我琴晚擺低左堆草俾佢<br />\n第二朝我發覺佢喺上面屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪代表呢款佢唔鍾意要買過新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剪完牙頭幾日要食草粉係正常架<br />\n疴尿係草上面我果隻閒唔時都會，不過我無理佢，還掂都要每日換草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最衰佢第一次有事個陣因爲當然同時有肺炎所以未可以麻醉剪牙住 當時食左成個月草粉<br />\n唔知係咪個陣佢習慣左食草粉<br />\n我有次問過醫生話佢淨係肯食草粉唔食糧<br />\n醫生叫我照擺糧同少少草粉<br />\n佢同我淨係食哂草粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗需要時間改番佢個習慣"}]}